yamli4xchat is a plugin to be used with XChat IRC Client, simply it use Yamli.com to convert arabic/english words to arabic words..

You need to make sure you have the following perl 2 modules before using this plugin:
* LWP::Simple
* JSON 

All what you have to do then is to load yamli4xchat.pl file within your XChat client (Window --> Plugins and Scripts --> Add)

Usage:

In the messeges tab, write /ya and whatever.. for example:

/ya alsalam 3lykom

<ME>  السلام عليكم


BTW, this created as testing and just for fun, so don't expect it works as you expect (between its slow!) 
